<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">KitBashers, this is Mission Control. We've discovered a new star system beyond the furthest reaches of our known universe: The Minerva Galaxy. This Kit will give you everything a spacefaring explorer needs to build your world in Minerva, from cargo ships, terrain rovers and terraformers to community centers and endless modular habitats. This is your opportunity to explore the deepest fields of your imagination. Be sure to tag your creation with #KB3Dchallenge when you post it to have your work be part of the galaxy! Have fun and good luck to you. </span></p>
